author: ijjk
message:
Revert "build: Update `swc_core` to `v24.0.0`" (#79102)

This seems to be failing to build on darwin still x-ref:
https://github.com/vercel/next.js/actions/runs/14978295541/job/42077365728

Reverts vercel/next.js#79092

-  "getrandom_backend=\"wasm_js\"",

         uses: ./.github/actions/setup-rust
         with:
-          targets: wasm32-wasip1
+          targets: wasm32-unknown-unknown
 
       - name: Install wasm-pack
         run: curl https://rustwasm.github.io/wasm-pack/installer/init.sh -sSf | sh
